{"prompt": "Generate a website for a smart home technology. The website should be dynamic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Smart Home Tech</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #c62828; /* Deep Red */\n            --secondary-color: #e57373; /* Lighter Red/Pinkish */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #f5f5f5;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--brand-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 0 2rem;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 2rem;\n            flex-wrap: wrap; /* Allow wrapping for responsiveness */\n        }\n\n        section:nth-of-type(even) {\n            flex-direction: row-reverse; /* Alternate layout for visual interest */\n        }\n\n        section img {\n            max-width: 40%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            flex-shrink: 0; /* Prevent image from shrinking */\n        }\n\n        section div {\n            flex-grow: 1; /* Allow text content to grow */\n            min-width: 250px; /* Ensure text area has a minimum width */\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            font-size: 2rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        button {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border: none;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n            margin-top: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n        }\n\n        /* Dynamic Effect */\n        .dynamic-element {\n            animation: pulse 2s infinite ease-in-out;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% {\n                transform: scale(1);\n                box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 var(--secondary-color);\n            }\n            70% {\n                transform: scale(1.05);\n                box-shadow: 0 0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\n            }\n            100% {\n                transform: scale(1);\n                box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\n            }\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive Design */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5rem;\n            }\n            section {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                text-align: center;\n            }\n            section img {\n                max-width: 80%;\n                margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            }\n            section:nth-of-type(even) {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Smart Home Revolution</h1>\n        <p>Experience the Future of Living, Effortlessly.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/c62828/ffffff?text=Smart+Hub\" alt=\"Smart Home Hub\">\n            <div>\n                <h2>Your Intelligent Home Command Center</h2>\n                <p>Our smart hub is the brain of your connected home. It seamlessly integrates all your devices, from lights and thermostats to security cameras and entertainment systems, providing intuitive control through a single app.</p>\n                <button>Learn More</button>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"features\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/e57373/ffffff?text=Automation\" alt=\"Automation Example\">\n            <div>\n                <h2>Automate Your Life</h2>\n                <p>Set custom routines and schedules to make your home work for you. Wake up to a gently lit room, have your coffee maker start automatically, and ensure your doors are locked at night \u2013 all without lifting a finger.</p>\n                <button class=\"dynamic-element\">Explore Automation</button>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"security\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/c62828/ffffff?text=Security\" alt=\"Smart Security System\">\n            <div>\n                <h2>Peace of Mind, Always</h2>\n                <p>Enhance your home's security with smart locks, motion sensors, and video monitoring. Receive real-time alerts on your phone and remotely control access to your home, ensuring your loved ones and property are always safe.</p>\n                <button>Secure Your Home</button>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Smart Home Tech. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple JavaScript for potential future interactivity\n        document.querySelectorAll('button').forEach(button => {\n            button.addEventListener('click', () => {\n                alert('Discovering more smart solutions!');\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}